ice spst In its first year of operation products traded on IntercontinentalExchanges overthecounter markets reached the following volume levels Crude oil and refined products billion barrels Natural gas trillion cubic feet Power billion megawatt hours Precious metals million goldequivalent ounces The total notional value of transactions on the Exchange in its first year was over billion During the same period volumes on the IPE acquired by Intercontinental the past summer reached the following levels Brent crude futures and options lots Gas oil futures and options lots Natural gas futures lots The total notional value of the million lots traded on IPE over the last twelve months was in excess of billion Market participation on the Exchange continues to expand at a rapid rate and currently includes over of the worlds largest energy and financial commodity firms making it one of the most widely distributed online professional marketplaces in the world Moreover over customers in over countries use IPEs markets on a regular basis Justin Rostant Enron Financial Trading Desk Phone Mobile Fax

FX Currency Long Descriptiosattached you will find the Product Long Descriptions for the FX products If you have any questions call me at jr Forwarded by Justin RostantHOUECT on AM From Carlos Alatorre ENRON AM To cc Subject LME last change Forwarded by Carlos AlatorreNAEnron on AM From Carlos Alatorre AM To cc Subject LME last change Sara Please find attached your approved document with a last minute change please take a look and let us know if you are OK with it Also you can find the GTC disclaimer essentially the same as for all internal products Please let us know your approval or comments Ill really appreciate your prompt response since as mentioned we need to have both documents ready on the system by noon today in order to have them uploaded into the database and ready for trading next Monday Thank you Carlos x

Heating Oil Options revised Cc you take a look at the two long descriptions for the Heating Oil Options products and provide me with any comments The language for the exercise period and for the Asian option is listed below The reason that during was used is because the exercise period for a Dec option is not until the end of Dec The calculation of the Index price is the average of the daily price for the month of Dec The Exercise Periods shall be the last Trading Day of the NYMEX Heating Oil Contract during the applicable Determination Period The Index for each Exercise Period shall be the simple arithmetic average of the daily settlement prices of the NYMEX Heating Oil Futures Contract for each Trading Day during the applicable Determination Period Attached are the Long Descriptions one has the changes highlighted and the other with the changes acceptedclean version Thanks jr

Heating Oil Options Long Description Cc is the Long Description for the Heating Oil Options The changes that are highlighted in this document were suggestions that you made Can you please reply confirming your agreement of the Long description Thanks jr

Nymex Cc Mark we are trying to get some information on the Nymex Access Electronic Trading System It is our understanding that during the day the electronic trading system cannot be used because all prices must be announced on the Trading floor so all members are aware of the prices at the same time However Nymex wants to use the Access system to post prices after trading hours Does EnronOnline have any legal obstacles to overcome if we want to post our prices on Access andor Nymex post their prices on EnronOnline Thank you in advance for your assistance Justin Rostant EnronOnline LLC Phone Mobile Fax
